    {
      "id": 85052,
      "post_number": 9,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-03-02T16:47:27.761Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Kam vite qe e kam parë. Më kujtohet qe eshte film koral, me shume personazhe kryesore njeheresh.<br>\nKam fol ngapak për ate periudhe të PTA, sidomos kur kemi evoku ketu “There Will be blood”. Nuk eshte tasi im i kafese ajo lloj të beri kinematografi po nejse.</p>\n<p>Pashe nje film të ri të mirë amerikan mbreme: larg të qenit perfect (aq më mirë xhanem!! Cili eshte perfect ne kete botë, qe të na qenkan filmat?) por shume ngazellyes (joyfull) dhe kolektiv: “Sorry to bother you”<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/heart_eyes.png?v=6\" title=\":heart_eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":heart_eyes:\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7643cf1b307b84b67ed6e8f2969654d1bbe60f6a.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"453\" height=\"640\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 7,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 85053,
      "post_number": 10,
      "username": "korriku",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/korriku/{size}/18544_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-03-02T17:00:52.144Z",
      "cooked": "<p>ja ta shohim - dmth gjendet kollaj</p>\n<p>e paski marre me zell kinemane afro-amerikane andej nga cahiers du cinema</p>\n<p>ps. levizja me e fuqishme sot ne usa eshte ajo pseudo e majte mbi ‘structural racism’, qe shkurt perkthehet ne tezen e lul bashes ik ti se e kam radhen une</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 9,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 85054,
      "post_number": 11,
      "username": "korriku",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/korriku/{size}/18544_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-03-02T17:41:39.933Z",
      "cooked": "<p>e megjithate e kam nje pyetje per punen e bretkosave</p>\n<p>duke te kuptuar lidhur me metaforen si pika qendrore ne film - meqe si film koral te gjitha ngjarjet konvergojne tek ‘bretkosat’ - si do ta dallonim nese ajo eshte e egzagjeruar ne ndryshim per shembull nga nje metafore qendrore e ngjajshme  te ‘Stillet licht’ e Reygadas, ta zeme - e cila edhe evokon Ordet</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 85076,
      "post_number": 12,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-03-02T22:32:16.189Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Magnolia eshte film i ‘rende’, peshon nje kuintal. Gati-gati edhe vizualisht :</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5bcaea27e9edb2419b18a4bf6a365c753a0198d4.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/5bcaea27e9edb2419b18a4bf6a365c753a0198d4\" title=\"magnolia6.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5bcaea27e9edb2419b18a4bf6a365c753a0198d4.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"332\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5bcaea27e9edb2419b18a4bf6a365c753a0198d4_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">magnolia6.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">900×374 89.9 KB</span><span class=\"expand\"></span>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/701a64009bccaca2d9f066e151ad2fb7b2956ce5.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"340\"></p>\n<p>ndersa Silent light eshte plote ajer, eshte ‘i lehte’:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/a89b0c779e2a277b8f33637dae85758435e7838b.jpeg\" width=\"448\" height=\"252\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3118f4dadf46d46318b8b4cab09204db94efd476.jpeg\" width=\"600\" height=\"239\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 11,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 85077,
      "post_number": 13,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2019-03-02T22:38:52.049Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Filmi në fjale ka dale me pikatore në France (25-30 kopje gjithesej, nderkohe qe mesatarja e filmave indipendente eshte, të pakten, 80-90).<br>\nE ke të kote fiksimin me ‘kinemane afro-amerikane’ (e cila esht thjesht nje <strong>gadget</strong> sikurse eshte Sundance, Oscar, Cannes etj, por kaq).</p>",
