      "created_at": "2019-03-02T23:45:13.301Z",
      "cooked": "<p>epo shume mire, ne nje film te rende si Magnolia edhe mrekullia vjen e rende si shpagim i natyres.<br>\nTek Stillet licht film i lehte plot ajer sic thua ti me te drejte, edhe mrekullia vjen si diell <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=6\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"><br>\nne te dyja rastet me duket funksionon.<br>\nvecse nese PTA e ka ndertuar filmin qellimisht per ate skene me bretkosat.<br>\nnejse … <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/crazy_face.png?v=6\" title=\":crazy_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":crazy_face:\"></p>\n<p>kete filmin amerikan m’u be se e pashe diku ne rrjet javes qe shkoi</p>",
